        {"label_en": "Banking & asset protection", "label_fr": "Banque et protection des avoirs",
         "description": "Banking access, account opening for non-citizens, asset-protection and financial-secrecy practices. Cite reputable financial sources."}
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "retiree",
