      "blurb_fr": "Vous préparez votre retraite. On regarde le visa, le coût de la vie, la santé et le climat.",
      "blurb_en": "You're relocating for retirement. We look at visa, cost of living, healthcare and climate.",
      "match": {"reasons": ["retirement"], "tags": ["retirement"]},
